      "local_index": 7,
      "narrator_chain": {
        "parts": [
          {
            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "ومنها ان"
          }
        ]
      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/kitab-al-ghayba-tusi:6:7",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/27/1/6/7",
      "text": [
        "قراض هذه الفرقة فإنه لم يبق في الدنيا في وقتنا ولا قبله بزمان طويل قائل يقول به، ولو كان ذلك حقا لما جاز انقراضه."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayyid-athar-husain-s-h-rizvi": [
          "Fourthly, this sect has become extinct. Not in our time, nor before us for a very long time, a believer of this creed has existed. If it were a true faith, its extinction would have been impossible."
        ]
      }
    },
    "verse_translations": [
      "en.sayyid-athar-husain-s-h-rizvi"
    ]
